<a class="question_link" target="_blank" href="/question/37956338/answer/74300982">如何评价有个猫奴说猫毛过敏是矫情，另外过敏测试多危险？</a>
</div>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
data-aid="25143679"
data-atoken="74300982"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1448680056"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="1"
data-copyable="1"
>
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-25143679"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-votecount="101">101</a>
</div>

